e just amazed with delight! Its money you have worked 100%. The animation is<br> excellent. All comments and changes were finalized in time. We now have a wonderful image site with<br> user-friendly interface and excellent opportunities for filling content. Great job! If you want the site was<br> not just, and that it makes a profit, SmartHameleon highly recommend!\\u00bb\\n\",\"button_text\":\"\",\"background_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"background_image\":{\"url\":\"\",\"id\":\"\"},\"background_size\":\"cover\",\"background_ken_burns\":\"\",\"zoom_direction\":\"in\",\"background_overlay\":\"\",\"background_overlay_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.5)\",\"background_overlay_blend_mode\":\"\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"link_click\":\"slide\",\"custom_style\":\"\",\"horizontal_position\":\"\",\"vertical_position\":\"\",\"text_align\":\"\",\"content_color\":\"\",\"repeater_text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"\",\"repeater_text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":0,\"blur\":10,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"},\"_id\":\"e13d657\"},{\"heading\":\"\",\"description\":\" We hired Smart Chameleon for their knowledge in the field of design. We have worked with them in the past with consultation  We decided to give them a try for a complete website rebranding. The work they did was outstanding! Although we had lots of ideas and changes that occurred while they worked on the project, we are thankful for their patience with us too! The new website has drastically increased in traffic and business! Parents now can easily reserve a party without calling and trying to figure out who is where and what is what, I received lots of compliments on that.  Besides design, we use smart chameleon for varies marketing purposes, like graphic design, digital marketing, and their new service business consultation.  I recommend them if you have a complex or intermediate project.\",\"button_text\":\"\",\"background_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"ba