(170, 1, '2020-06-09 10:57:34', '2020-06-09 08:57:34', '<img width=\"276\" height=\"66\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Logo.png\" alt=\"\" />											\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\" id=\"BTN1\">\n						START A PROJECT\n					</a>\n			<h2>CLIENTS ABOUT US</h2>		\n					«When we discussed what should be our site, we have little idea of what should eventually turn out. We<br> made this site, we were just amazed with delight! Its money you have worked 100%. The animation is<br> excellent. All comments and changes were finalized in time. We now have a wonderful image site with<br> user-friendly interface and excellent opportunities for filling content. Great job! If you want the site was<br> not just, and that it makes a profit, SmartHameleon highly recommend!»\n We hired Smart Chameleon for their knowledge in the field of design. We have worked with them in the past with consultation  We decided to give them a try for a complete website rebranding. The work they did was outstanding! Although we had lots of ideas and changes that occurred while they worked on the project, we are thankful for their patience with us too! The new website has drastically increased in traffic and business! Parents now can easily reserve a party without calling and trying to figure out who is where and what is what, I received lots of compliments on that.  Besides design, we use smart chameleon for varies marketing purposes, like graphic design, digital marketing, and their new service business consultation.  I recommend them if you have a complex or intermediate project. «I want to express my great gratitude for the work done. Now the new face of our company is just great! Site, logo, corporate identity - everything is very cool! I liked the easy, light design, everything is very stylish, understandable and informative. The survey of our customers for 2016 was designed very successfully - it turned out creatively. Advertising is set up very competently, now it all works several times more efficiently.\nI am really happy with the result!» «I did my first lending page by myself with the help of one of online services. Six months later I realized that there was many things to change in order to bring my business to new level. I come to these guys and I worried that they would have do not exactly what I wanted! I sell services, entertainment! The site should catch the eye, cause great emotions! What has happened, they exceeded all my expectations! I can say \"hit the bull\'s-eye\"! Many modern points attract customers and motivate them to buy. The site really works, and I make profit! Thank you!!!» «They were so involved in the situation, that sometimes I felt uncomfortable, because the price for the work that they promised me to do compared to similar companies was 30-40% lower!\nI was worried - will they understand what do I want from them? etc... But the time has come, and they showed me the finished layout. I was really impressed! It turned out CHICLY, MODERN, CONVENIENT for the client! Honestly, I still believe that Benjamin (art director) has an art of reading thoughts, - so accurately he got into my idea of what I want and how it should look for our customers!&nbsp;\nResult: the conversion on the new site became 9 times higher!» «The site came out very stylish and modern, but most importantly - effective! Very cool! Exactly what we wanted. Lightness and ease in design, along with a powerful offer, have done their job: we getting customers through the Internet. It took a long time for advertising and finalizing campaign, but the end result met all expectations. Thank you very much for your excellent work!»				\n							Previous\n							Next\n										<img width=\"580\" height=\"485\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/bg-laptop2-768x642.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/bg-laptop2-768x642.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/06